 \r\n\r\nRecognize the danger and act accordingly, because their next target just might be you. The left is in open war with us.", "author": "AmannamedRJ", "created": 1777263656848, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "BlackJack1776", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Did you notice it?", "last_comment_created": 1777265631400, "content": "<p>It was very subtle, but the 60 Minutes interview cinched it. Previously, when an assassination or attempt by a leftist transpired, the MSM would play some level of lip service to a commitment toward non-violence. Before, they'd leave their hairbrained conspiracies to the lunatics online.</p>\n<p>Not today:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Unfunny Faggot Jimmy Kimmel mocks Melania for having the &quot;glow of a widow&quot; - mocking her and Erika Kirk</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>60 minutes runs an interview where Norah O'Donnell reads aloud an attempted murderer's manifesto as a proxy to allege Trump is a rapist and pedophile to his face - then plays dumb when he grills her ass on it.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The MSM, that is to say, the cosmopolitan left is putting out programming that de-facto condones political assassinations, and moving forward they will no longer shed any false sympathies. Leftwing political murder is now normalized. There can be no more debates the Left and <em>all of it's institutions</em> fully support political violence against the right.</p>\n<p>Recognize the danger and act accordingly, because their next target just might be you. The left is in open war with us.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 21, 